author: fnathan
title: Real Sociedad 0 Barcelona 1: Barca take aggregate advantage into Copa del Rey quarter-final second leg thanks to Neymar penalty
text: EFL kings in the cup Real Sociedad 0 Barcelona 1: Barca take aggregate advantage into Copa del Rey quarter-final second leg thanks to Neymar penalty Lionel Messi, Luis Suarez and Neymar all play as Luis Enrique's side face fifth placd Sociedad with both sides aiming for the last four of the Spanish Cup Was 1-0 at half time from the Anoeta thanks to Neymar's 21st minute penalty, which he won himself Second half did not see Sociedad threaten at all Listen to Real Sociedad v Barcelona on talkSPORT HERE Read our match report HERE Live Blog
